Say: "If Allah had been with the conclusive religion, He would have guided you all."
Say (O Muhammad SAW): "Bring your witnesses, if you bear witness to their witnesses, so do not bear witness against them, and do not bear witness to them who deny Our signs and who do not believe in the Hereafter.
Say (O Muhammad SAW): "Show me what your Lord has forbidden you. Say: 'Do not associate anything with Him, and be good to your parents, and do not kill your children. Do not kill your children. Do not kill your children, and do not kill them. This is what God has given you. That is what He has revealed to you. This is what God has given you.
